Invocation Name: life tracker
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Start with a simple character and by completing your daily tasks, build your characters level, skills, armor, weapons, mounts and much more. Join over 2.5 million people whare are already improving their lives, one task at a time, and having a lot of fun while doing it. 

This app provides a voice interface for tracking your tasks and gaining levels through Habitica.com.
